<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include("includes/head", { title: 'NOC Application Form' }) %>
    
    <!-- link to stylesheet -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/noc-form.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <%- include("includes/main-header") %> 
      <%- include("includes/nav-header") %>
    </header>

    <main>
      <h3 id="noc-form-heading">
        Student Internship Request form for
        <strong>No Objection Certificate (NOC)</strong>
      </h3>

      <div id="instructions">
        <h4 id="instructions-main-heading">Instructions</h4>

        <h5 id="instructions-sub-heading">
          Do read all instruction carefully mentioned below
        </h5>

        <div>
          <p>
            Dear Students,
            <br />
            All the students, whoever is going for any Internship / Project /
            Training in any Organization, are required to take
            <strong> NO OBJECTION CERTFICATE (NOC) </strong>
            for the same.
            <br />
            <br />
            Do follow the procedure of applying online:-
            <br />
          </p>

          <ol>
            <li>
              Take care of information you are providing in the online form
              which will be printed as it is in the NOC for Internship/Training.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Very Important:</strong>
              Do confirm and write carefully the Name, Designation and Company
              Name & Address in the form to whom you are sending letter/NOC in
              that company/organization. It will be printed as it is. If you do
              mistake in writing spelling of any name, designation or company
              name, it will not be accepted any where. Even a minor mistake of
              Comma (,) will not be considered.
            </li>
            <li>
              You will receive NOC via Email through T&P Cell. It will be an
              automatically generated letter/NOC with date and reference number
              after approval of your Faculty Coordinator/Internship Coordinator
              of your Department and then from T&P Cell. For further proofs you
              can directly take the print of email with all details and live
              link of NOC at our drive if any further proof is required by any
              organization.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <p>
            <strong
              >IMPORTANT NOTE: Do Read each and every instruction given in the
              Online Form and below each field</strong
            >
            <br />
            <br />
            For any query: You may contact to your Faculty Coordinator.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="NOC-form-container">
        <h4 id="noc-form-sub-heading">Student's personal details</h4>
        <form action="/organization-details.html" method="GET">
          <ul id="input-fields-list">
            <li>
              <label for="student-email">Email</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="student-email"
                name="student-email"
                placeholder="Your Email"
                required
              />
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="student-enrollment-no">Enrollment Number</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="student-enrollment-no"
                name="student-enrollment-no"
                placeholder="Your Enrollment Number"
                required
              />
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="student-name"
                >Name
                <br />
                <span class="extra-instructions"
                  >(Write your official name present on documents. First Letter
                  of each word should be in CAPITAL)</span
                ></label
              >
              <input
                type="text"
                id="student-name"
                name="student-name"
                placeholder="Your Name"
                required
              />
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="student-mobile">Mobile Number</label>
              <input
                type="tel"
                id="student-mobile"
                name="student-mobile"
                placeholder="Your Mobile Number"
                maxlength="10"
                minlength="10"
                required
              />
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="student-father-name">Father's Name</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="student-father-name"
                name="student-father-name"
                placeholder="Your Father's Name"
                required
              />
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="branch">Branch</label>
              <select name="branch" id="branch" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected hidden>
                  Choose Your Branch
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Civil Engineering">
                  B.Tech - Civil Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Mechanical Engineering">
                  B.Tech - Mechanical Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Electrical Engineering">
                  B.Tech - Electrical Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Electronics Engineering">
                  B.Tech - Electronics Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Computer Science & Engineering">
                  B.Tech - Computer Science & Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Chemical Engineering">
                  B.Tech - Chemical Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Information Technology">
                  B.Tech - Information Technology
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Biotechnology">
                  B.Tech - Biotechnology
                </option>
                <option
                  value="B.Tech - Electronics & Telecommunication Engineering"
                >
                  B.Tech - Electronics & Telecommunication Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech - Automobile Engineering">
                  B.Tech - Automobile Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="MCA">MCA</option>
                <option value="MBA">MBA</option>
                <option value="B.Tech- Artificial Intelligence and Robotics">
                  B.Tech- Artificial Intelligence and Robotics
                </option>
                <option value="B.Tech- Mathematics and Computing">
                  B.Tech- Mathematics and Computing
                </option>
                <option
                  value="B.Tech- Internet of Things (Offered by Electrical Engineering Department)"
                >
                  B.Tech- Internet of Things (Offered by Electrical Engineering
                  Department)
                </option>
                <option
                  value="B.Tech- Internet of Things (IOT) (Offered by Information Technology Department)"
                >
                  B.Tech- Internet of Things (IOT) (Offered by Information
                  Technology Department)
                </option>
              </select>
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="department">Department</label>
              <select name="department" id="department" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected hidden>
                  Choose Your Department
                </option>
                <option value="Civil Engineering">Civil Engineering</option>
                <option value="Mechanical Engineering & Automobile">
                  Mechanical Engineering & Automobile
                </option>
                <option value="Electrical Engineering">
                  Electrical Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="Electronics Engineering & ET">
                  Electronics Engineering & ET
                </option>
                <option value="Computer Science & Engineering & MCA">
                  Computer Science & Engineering & MCA
                </option>
                <option value="Mathematics and Computing">
                  Mathematics and Computing
                </option>
                <option value="Chemical Engineering">
                  Chemical Engineering
                </option>
                <option value="Information Technology">
                  Information Technology
                </option>
                <option value="Biotechnology">Biotechnology</option>
                <option value="MBA">MBA</option>
              </select>
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="year">Year</label>
              <select name="year" id="year" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected hidden>Choose Year</option>
                <option value="II Year Btech">II Year Btech</option>
                <option value="Pre Final Year B.Tech/ MCA/ MBA">
                  Pre Final Year B.Tech/ MCA/ MBA
                </option>
                <option value="Final Year B.Tech / MCA/ MBA">
                  Final Year B.Tech / MCA/ MBA
                </option>
              </select>
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="student-current-address">Current Address</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="student-current-address"
                name="student-current-address"
                placeholder="Your Current Address"
                required
              />
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="student-city">City</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="student-city"
                name="student-city"
                placeholder="Your City"
                required
              />
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="student-state">State</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="student-state"
                name="student-state"
                placeholder="Your State"
                required
              />
            </li>
            <li>
              <label for="student-pincode">PIN Code</label>
              <input
                type="number"
                id="student-pincode"
                name="student-pincode"
                placeholder="Your PIN Code"
                min="100000"
                max="999999"
                required
              />
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div id="button-container">
            <button type="reset" class="btn-alt">Clear Form</button>
            <button type="submit" class="btn">Next</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <%- include("includes/footer") %>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
